Posts.Content: Jsut9802 wrote: I wanted to start a new thread for those of us in our 30s. I was diagnosed Jan 6th, just a few weeks before turning 37. I will be starting treatment (chemo, dose dense ac-T) next week. I am a "healthy", fun and athletic mom of a 10 year old and am looking to chat with others in the same boat. Dx 1/6/2017, DCIS/IDC, Left, 4cm, Stage IIB, Grade 2, 2/21 nodes, ER+/PR+, HER2- Hormonal Therapy 2/2/2017 Tamoxifen pills (Nolvadex, Apo-Tamox, Tamofen, Tamone) Log in to post a reply
